column2: [not maintained] Lightweight JavaScript library operating system for the cloud

column5:
Merge pull request #133 from runtimejs/disk-driver

Disk driver!
runtime.disk -> runtime.block, improved device access structure, minor fixes
The disk API makes more sense now
Use int64-buffer for disk sector ops

Merge pull request #128 from runtimejs/v8-flags

Allow V8 flags to be configured at runtime

Merge pull request #120 from runtimejs/code-style

Update everything to ES6 and adopt a code style

Merge pull request #124 from runtimejs/v8

V8 5.4.9
Fix typo, add a note, add some extra wording
Add feature request section, update link to code style exceptions
